    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1912-09-26T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1912-09-26T00:00:00-05:00" n="1516"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1516">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 817.51/505.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the <gloss type="to">American Minister</gloss>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1912-09-26">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 26, 1912</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>The following just received from the bankers: <quote rend="blockquote">
                        <p>The plan we submitted, and accepted by Nicaragua, involved no delay and
                            will, we trust, be promptly adopted.</p>
                    </quote>
                </p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Wilson.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
